metadata.name: Golden Torus 2x7
metadata.description:
Star is a hyperdimensional artwork that consists of 468 unique Shards that provide access to energetic benefits and exclusive spaces for co-creation and education within our Ternion Earth Universe.

Become a Ternion Earth Shard Holder and unlock the following benefits:

1. Receive the individual healing, empowering, and protecting energies of your Shard  
2. Participate in crystal technology co-creation opportunities based on your Shard's Ray 
3. Join exclusive educational offerings based on your Shard's Source

Let us join forces and work together to ensure that humanity rises to the new challenges and shifts to higher consciousness.
